             was indicted for <rs id="t17810425-47-off228" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17810425-47-off228" type="offenceCategory" value="sexual"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17810425-47-off228" type="offenceSubcategory" value="rape"></interp>
               feloniously committing a rape on the body of Penelope, the <rs id="t17810425-47-viclabel229" type="occupation">wife</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17810425-47-victim483 t17810425-47-viclabel229"></join> of 
